<div class="banner banner-become-host">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row mt-2">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h1>Become a tiny host today and start making a fortune!</h1>
        <br>
        <br>
        <p>No matter what kind of tiny home or room you have to share, TinyBnb makes it simple and secure to host travellers. You’re in full control of your availability, prices, house rules, and how you interact with guests.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="search-form">
          <h1>Enter your flat details here</h1>
          <%= simple_form_for @flat do |f| %>
            <%= f.input :title %>
            <%= f.input :description, placeholder: "Write something sexy" %>
            <%= f.input :address %>
            <div class="form-row fg justify-content-between">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <%= f.input :guests %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <%= f.input :bedrooms %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <%= f.input :beds %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <%= f.input :price_per_night %>
            <%= f.input :photos, as: :file, input_html: {multiple: true} %>
            <%= f.submit "Add my tiny house", class: "btn btn-danger" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
<br>
<h1>Hosting in three steps</h1>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row how-it-works">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="mt-3 how-text">
        <i class="far fa-check-circle"></i>
        <h2 class="mt-3">List your space for free</h2>
        <p>Share any space without sign-up charges, from a shared living room to a second home and everything in-between.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="mt-3 how-text">
        <i class="far fa-check-circle"></i>
        <h2 class="mt-3">Decide how you want to host</h2>
        <p>Choose your own schedule, prices, and requirements for guests. We’re there to help along the way.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="mt-3 how-text">
        <i class="far fa-check-circle"></i>
        <h2 class="mt-3">Welcome your first guest</h2>
        <p>Once your listing is live, qualified guests can reach out. You can message them with any questions before their stay.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class=" banner host-banner-two">
      <div class="text-host-banner">
        <h1>Become a tiny host and start earning today</h1>
        <p>Join the fastest growing network of tiny flats</p>
        <p><%= link_to "Start earning today", new_flat_path, class: "host-button-two btn btn-danger mt-4" %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>






















